{
  "$comment": "Maps each data adapter to the PRANA/SoapBox component that consumes it. An adapter is any *.mjs in this dir tree (recursing one level into topic subdirs like legal/ library/ media/), excluding *.test.mjs and the linter itself. Top-level adapters are keyed by bare filename; nested adapters by their POSIX path ('legal/courtlistener.mjs'). check-consumer-matrix.mjs fails CI if an adapter has no consumer here, or if this file names an adapter that does not exist. 'component' is a generic role name, not a brand.",
